<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="companion-n">companion <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kəm'pæniən/    美 /kəm'pæniən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 同伴；伴侣；旅伴：</strong></h4>
<p>a person or animal with whom you spend a lot of time or go somewhere：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a travelling / drinking / dinner companion 
旅伴/酒友/饭友</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The dog may be a good companion for the old. 
对老人而言，狗也许是很好的伙伴。</p><footer>2012 天津</footer></div></div>